<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>백테스팅 — 스윙 점수 검증</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js@4.4.1/dist/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
  <style>
    :root {
      --brand-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #6366f1 100%);
      --soft-bg: #f3f5fb;
      --muted: #64748b;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--soft-bg);
      color: #1f2937;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Apple SD Gothic Neo", "Malgun Gothic", sans-serif;
    }
    .app-header {
      background: var(--brand-gradient);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 28px 0 56px;
      margin-bottom: -40px;
    }
    .app-header h1 { font-weight: 700; margin: 0; font-size: 1.5rem; }
    .app-header .subtitle { opacity: 0.85; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 4px; }
    .glass-card {
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      background: #fff;
    }
    .stat-cell {
      background: #f8fafc;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
    }
    .stat-cell .label { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.72rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.4px; }
    .stat-cell .value { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; margin-top: 4px; }
    .pos { color: #16a34a; }
    .neg { color: #dc2626; }
    .table thead th { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); }
    .table tbody td { vertical-align: middle; font-size: 0.86rem; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
    .horizon-card {
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 14px;
      background: #fff;
    }
    .horizon-card .h-title {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1e293b;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .info-box {
      border-left: 3px solid #6366f1;
      background: #eef2ff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: #1e293b;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="app-header">
    <div class="container-fluid px-3 px-lg-5 d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start gap-3 flex-wrap">
      <div>
        <h1><i class="bi bi-clipboard-data me-2"></i>백테스팅</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">스윙 점수 모델 (10요소, flow 제외, 추세 추종 포함) 의 과거 적중률 검증</div>
      </div>
      <div class="d-flex gap-2 align-self-center flex-wrap">
        <button type="button" onclick="history.back()" class="btn btn-light btn-sm">
          <i class="bi bi-arrow-left me-1"></i>이전
        </button>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-light btn-sm"><i class="bi bi-house me-1"></i>딥다이브</a>
        <a href="/scan" class="btn btn-light btn-sm"><i class="bi bi-radar me-1"></i>스캔</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="container-fluid px-3 px-lg-5 pb-5">
    <!-- 입력 폼 -->
    <div class="glass-card p-3 p-lg-4 mb-4">
      <form method="post" action="/backtest" class="row g-3 align-items-end">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-3">
          <label class="form-label small text-secondary mb-1">종목 (이름 또는 코드)</label>
          <input type="text" name="query" class="form-control form-control-sm"
                 value="<%= options.query %>" placeholder="예: 삼성전자 또는 005930" required />
        </div>
        <div class="col-6 col-md-2">
          <label class="form-label small text-secondary mb-1" title="얼마나 과거까지 검증할지 (3~24개월)">
            기간 (개월)
          </label>
          <input type="number" name="monthsBack" class="form-control form-control-sm"
                 value="<%= options.monthsBack %>" min="3" max="24" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-6 col-md-2">
          <label class="form-label small text-secondary mb-1" title="이 점수 이상인 날에 매수 시뮬">
            점수 임계치
          </label>
          <input type="number" name="threshold" class="form-control form-control-sm"
                 value="<%= options.threshold %>" min="0" max="100" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-3">
          <label class="form-label small text-secondary mb-1">보유 기간 (일)</label>
          <div class="d-flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <% [5, 10, 20, 40].forEach(function(h) { %>
              <div class="form-check">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="horizons" value="<%= h %>"
                       id="h<%= h %>" <%= options.horizons.includes(h) ? "checked" : "" %> />
                <label class="form-check-label small" for="h<%= h %>"><%= h %>일</label>
              </div>
            <% }); %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-2 text-md-end">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm w-100">
            <i class="bi bi-play-fill me-1"></i>백테스트 실행
          </button>
        </div>
      </form>
      <div class="info-box mt-3">
        <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-1"></i>
        매 거래일에 <strong>그날까지의 데이터만으로</strong> 점수를 다시 계산해 (look-ahead 방지)
        임계치 이상이면 그날 종가 매수 → N일 후 종가 청산을 가정합니다.
        <strong>flow 점수는 제외</strong>한 10요소 (volume / position / trend / trendFollow / rsi / macd / resistance / volatility / dryUp / squeeze) 가중합 100점에서
        <strong>단기 폭등 페널티</strong>(5일 +10/15/20/25% 시 -5/-10/-15/-20점) 차감.
      </div>
    </div>

    <% if (error) { %>
      <div class="glass-card p-3 mb-4">
        <div class="alert alert-danger small mb-0">
          <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle me-1"></i><%= error %>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% } %>

    <% if (candidates && candidates.length > 1) { %>
      <div class="glass-card p-3 mb-4">
        <div class="alert alert-warning small mb-0">
          <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-1"></i>
          '<strong><%= options.query %></strong>' 검색 결과 <strong><%= candidates.length %>개</strong>가 일치합니다.
          첫 번째 <strong><%= candidates[0].name %> (<%= candidates[0].shortCode %>)</strong>로 백테스트했습니다.
          다른 종목으로 보려면 코드를 직접 입력하세요:
          <div class="mt-2 d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <% candidates.forEach(function(c, i) { %>
              <a href="/backtest?query=<%= encodeURIComponent(c.shortCode) %>&months=<%= options.monthsBack %>&threshold=<%= options.threshold %>&horizons=<%= options.horizons.join(',') %>"
                 class="badge bg-light text-dark text-decoration-none border <%= i === 0 ? 'border-primary' : '' %>">
                <%= c.name %> · <%= c.shortCode %> · <%= c.market %>
              </a>
            <% }); %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% } %>

    <% if (result) { %>
      <!-- 종목 + 시그널 요약 -->
      <div class="glass-card p-3 p-lg-4 mb-4">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center flex-wrap gap-2">
          <div>
            <h2 class="h5 mb-1">
              <%= result.stockMeta.name %>
              <span class="text-secondary small ms-2"><%= result.stockMeta.shortCode %> · <%= result.stockMeta.market %></span>
              <% if (result.stockType === 'weakTrend') { %>
                <span style="display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:#e0e7ff;color:#4338ca;font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:600;margin-left:6px;vertical-align:middle;"
                      title="60일 박스권 또는 V자 회복 도중 — 추세 추종 모델 신뢰도 낮음. 박스권 매매 관점으로 보세요.">
                  📊 박스권
                </span>
              <% } %>
            </h2>
            <div class="small text-secondary">
              검증 기간 <%= result.monthsBack %>개월 · 거래일 <%= result.series.length %>일 ·
              임계치 <%= result.threshold %> 이상 시그널 <strong><%= result.signals.length %></strong>건
            </div>
          </div>
          <form method="POST" action="/search" class="m-0">
            <input type="hidden" name="stockQuery" value="<%= result.stockMeta.shortCode %>" />
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm">
              <i class="bi bi-graph-up me-1"></i>이 종목 딥다이브
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>

        <% if (result.signals.length === 0) { %>
          <div class="alert alert-warning small mt-3 mb-0">
            <i class="bi bi-exclamation-circle me-1"></i>
            임계치 <%= result.threshold %> 이상인 시그널이 없습니다. 임계치를 낮춰보거나 기간을 늘려 보세요.
          </div>
        <% } %>
      </div>

      <% if (result.signals.length > 0) { %>
        <!-- horizon별 통계 -->
        <div class="glass-card p-3 p-lg-4 mb-4">
          <h2 class="h6 mb-3"><i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow me-1"></i>보유 기간별 결과</h2>
          <div class="row g-3">
            <% result.horizonResults.forEach(function(hr) { %>
              <div class="col-md-<%= 12 / result.horizonResults.length %>">
                <div class="horizon-card">
                  <div class="h-title">H = <%= hr.horizon %>일 보유</div>
                  <div class="row g-2">
                    <div class="col-6">
                      <div class="stat-cell">
                        <div class="label">매매</div>
                        <div class="value"><%= hr.n %>회</div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6">
                      <div class="stat-cell">
                        <div class="label">승률</div>
                        <div class="value"><%= hr.winRate.toFixed(1) %>%</div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6">
                      <div class="stat-cell">
                        <div class="label">평균 수익</div>
                        <div class="value <%= hr.avgReturn >= 0 ? 'pos' : 'neg' %>">
                          <%= (hr.avgReturn >= 0 ? '+' : '') + hr.avgReturn.toFixed(2) %>%
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6">
                      <div class="stat-cell">
                        <div class="label">누적 수익</div>
                        <div class="value <%= hr.cumulativeReturn >= 0 ? 'pos' : 'neg' %>">
                          <%= (hr.cumulativeReturn >= 0 ? '+' : '') + hr.cumulativeReturn.toFixed(1) %>%
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                      <div class="stat-cell">
                        <div class="label">최대 손실 (단일)</div>
                        <div class="value neg"><%= hr.mdd.toFixed(2) %>%</div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            <% }); %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 가격 + 점수 시계열 차트 -->
        <div class="glass-card p-3 p-lg-4 mb-4">
          <h2 class="h6 mb-3"><i class="bi bi-bar-chart-line me-1"></i>가격 / 점수 시계열 + 매수 시그널</h2>
          <canvas id="priceScoreChart" height="120"></canvas>
        </div>

        <!-- 매매 내역 (가장 긴 horizon 기준) -->
        <div class="glass-card p-3 p-lg-4 mb-4">
          <%
            const longest = result.horizonResults[result.horizonResults.length - 1];
          %>
          <h2 class="h6 mb-3">
            <i class="bi bi-list-ul me-1"></i>매매 내역
            <span class="text-secondary small ms-2">(H = <%= longest.horizon %>일 기준, <%= longest.n %>건)</span>
          </h2>
          <div class="table-responsive">
            <table class="table table-sm align-middle">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th>#</th>
                  <th>매수일</th>
                  <th class="text-end">매수가</th>
                  <th class="text-end">점수</th>
                  <th>청산일</th>
                  <th class="text-end">청산가</th>
                  <th class="text-end">수익률</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <% longest.trades.forEach(function(t, i) { %>
                  <tr>
                    <td><%= i + 1 %></td>
                    <td><%= t.entryDate %></td>
                    <td class="text-end"><%= t.entryPrice.toLocaleString() %></td>
                    <td class="text-end"><%= t.score %></td>
                    <td><%= t.exitDate %></td>
                    <td class="text-end"><%= t.exitPrice.toLocaleString() %></td>
                    <td class="text-end <%= t.returnPct >= 0 ? 'pos' : 'neg' %>">
                      <%= (t.returnPct >= 0 ? '+' : '') + t.returnPct.toFixed(2) %>%
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                <% }); %>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>

        <script>
          (function() {
            var labels = <%- JSON.stringify(result.series.map(s => s.date)) %>;
            var prices = <%- JSON.stringify(result.series.map(s => s.closePrice)) %>;
            var scores = <%- JSON.stringify(result.series.map(s => s.totalScore)) %>;
            var sigSet = new Set(<%- JSON.stringify(result.signals.map(s => s.date)) %>);
            var sigPoints = labels.map(function(d, i) { return sigSet.has(d) ? prices[i] : null; });

            var ctx = document.getElementById('priceScoreChart').getContext('2d');
            new Chart(ctx, {
              type: 'line',
              data: {
                labels: labels,
                datasets: [
                  {
                    label: '종가',
                    data: prices,
                    borderColor: '#0ea5e9',
                    backgroundColor: 'rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.05)',
                    borderWidth: 1.6,
                    pointRadius: 0,
                    yAxisID: 'y',
                    tension: 0.1,
                  },
                  {
                    label: '점수',
                    data: scores,
                    borderColor: '#6366f1',
                    borderDash: [4, 4],
                    borderWidth: 1.2,
                    pointRadius: 0,
                    yAxisID: 'y1',
                    tension: 0.1,
                  },
                  {
                    label: '매수 시그널',
                    data: sigPoints,
                    borderColor: 'transparent',
                    backgroundColor: '#dc2626',
                    pointRadius: 5,
                    pointHoverRadius: 7,
                    showLine: false,
                    yAxisID: 'y',
                  },
                ]
              },
              options: {
                responsive: true,
                interaction: { mode: 'index', intersect: false },
                scales: {
                  x: { ticks: { maxTicksLimit: 10, autoSkip: true } },
                  y:  { position: 'left',  title: { display: true, text: '가격' } },
                  y1: { position: 'right', title: { display: true, text: '점수' }, grid: { drawOnChartArea: false }, min: 0, max: 100 },
                }
              }
            });
          })();
        </script>
      <% } %>
    <% } %>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
